---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Professional Agent">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Agents: Pioneering the Future While Preserving the Present</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Shape the next chapter of entertainment while protecting your clients' interests</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Vision</h2>
                <p>In an industry constantly transformed by technology, agents face a crucial question: How do we embrace innovation while protecting and enhancing the careers of today's talent? "Living with the Ghost of Sam" offers a unique opportunity to help shape the answer, presenting a framework for responsible technological advancement that expands opportunities rather than replacing them.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card opportunity">
                <h2>A New Revenue Stream, Not a Replacement</h2>
                <p>Imagine being able to tell your clients that you're not just protecting their current interests - you're developing entirely new markets for their talents. Digital legacy management represents an expansion of the entertainment landscape, not a replacement of existing structures.</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Technology-Performance Synergy</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Living actors remain central to the narrative</li>
                        <li>AI enhancement serves the story rather than driving it</li>
                        <li>Digital recreations complement rather than compete with current talent</li>
                        <li>New roles emerge for technical advisors and performance consultants</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card opportunities">
                <h2>New Opportunities for Current Talent</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>For Actors:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Dual roles interacting with digital recreations</li>
                            <li>New performance techniques combining traditional and digital methods</li>
                            <li>Pioneering hybrid performance styles</li>
                            <li>Character development alongside AI enhancement</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Emerging Technical Roles:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Performance consultants</li>
                            <li>Digital asset managers</li>
                            <li>AI interaction specialists</li>
                            <li>Legacy preservation experts</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card protection">
                <h2>Protected Interests, Enhanced Opportunities</h2>
                <p>We understand the concerns about AI in entertainment. That's why this project emphasizes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Strict limitations to posthumous recreation with estate approval</li>
                    <li>Clear boundaries between digital recreation and live performance</li>
                    <li>Enhanced protections for performer likeness rights</li>
                    <li>New revenue streams for current performers who choose to participate</li>
                    <li>Additional employment opportunities in emerging technical roles</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card business-case">
                <h2>The Business Case</h2>
                <p>The numbers speak to expanding opportunities rather than replacement:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Historical precedent shows new technology creates more entertainment jobs</li>
                    <li>Digital recreation projects require larger, more diverse production teams</li>
                    <li>Hybrid performances command premium compensation</li>
                    <li>New technical roles offer additional representation opportunities</li>
                    <li>Estate management becomes an ongoing revenue stream</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Materials</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}scripts`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Scripts</h3>
                            <p>Access full episode scripts</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}bible`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Character Bible</h3>
                            <p>Detailed character backgrounds and development</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Shape the Future of Entertainment</h2>
                <p>Ready to be part of entertainment's next chapter while protecting your clients' interests?</p>
                <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="contact-btn">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
